SDL_DELAY函数在SDL源代码中定义在`src/timer/unix/SDL_timer.c`（对于Unix/Linux）和`src/timer/windows/SDL_systimer.c`（对于Windows）两个文件中。

在Unix/Linux系统上，`SDL_DELAY`函数的实现位于`src/timer/unix/SDL_timer.c`文件中，其中的具体定义如下：
```c
void
SDL_Delay(Uint32 ms)
{
    struct timespec elapsed, tv;
    Uint32 then, now, elapsed_ms;

    /* Set the timeout interval */
    then = SDL_GetTicks();
    elapsed_ms = then + ms;
    elapsed.tv_sec = ms / 1000;
    elapsed.tv_nsec = (ms % 1000) * 1000000;

    /* Wait for the timeout to expire */
    do {
        int retval = nanosleep(&elapsed, &tv);
        if (retval == 0) {
            break;
        }
        /* The only value we're truly interested in is EINTR, */
        /* If somebody wants to investigate the affects of other */
        /* signals on your code, please check the appropriate */
        /* documentation. --ryan. */
    } while (errno == EINTR);

    now = SDL_GetTicks();
    if (now < elapsed_ms) {
        SDL_SetError("SDL_Delay: Not enough time elapsed");
    }
}
```

在Windows系统上，`SDL_DELAY`函数的实现位于`src/timer/windows/SDL_systimer.c`文件中，具体定义如下：
```c
static void WIN_SetTimerResolution(DWORD ms_resolution);
static void WIN_RestoreTimerResolution(void);

void
SDL_Delay(Uint32 ms)
{
    DWORD then;
    Uint32 elapsed;

    then = timeGetTime();
    while ((elapsed = (timeGetTime()-then)) < ms) {
        Sleep(ms - elapsed);
    }
}
```

根据目标平台的不同，SDL_Delay函数在不同的源码文件中实现。
